title: Labor Income in Mining, Manufacturing, Construction and Agriculture for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1929-1946 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1946-1966. The Data Represent Commodity Producing Industries, Component Of Personal And Are Monthly Totals At Annual Rate. Source: Survey Of Current Business, August 1965.

This NBER data series m08273b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
